We may upon request, provide curbside pick-up and no-contact delivery. We are taking extreme precautions to make sure our community stays safe and healthy. We hope everybody stays safe and follow simple safety practices such as washing your hands frequently. We appreciate your understanding as well as your support. As the strong, tight-knit community that we are, we are extremely certain that we will ALL get through this. We thank you for your support throughout the years. #PizzaPlace #WeWillGetThroughThis
